article_title: Kibbutz confirms resident was killed in 7 October attacks.
sentence: Kibbutz  Nir  Yitzhak  has  overnight  confirmed  that  41-year-old  resident  Tal  Chaimi  was  killed  by  Hamas  in  the  7  October  attacks  in  southern  Israel.
